&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt;About Pluribus Digital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:281,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:281}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;At&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Pluribus Digital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;, we believe in fostering a dynamic and collaborative work environment where innovation thrives. As we pursue our mission to redefine the future of digital solutions, we seek passionate individuals who share our commitment to excellence and embody our core values:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;integrity, collaboration, and continuous learning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are not just a team — we are a community of forward-thinkers dedicated to pushing boundaries and creating meaningful impact for government agencies and the people they serve. If you are driven by&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge&amp;nbsp;technology, collaborative problem-solving, and&amp;nbsp;a strong sense&amp;nbsp;of purpose, you may be the ideal candidate to join our Pluribus Digital family.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Together,&amp;nbsp;let’s&amp;nbsp;shape the future of digital innovation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced&lt;strong&gt; Lead&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;DevOps Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to lead the design, governance, and evolution of enterprise cloud architecture within a federal environment. This role focuses on &lt;strong&gt;architectural leadership, strategic planning, and technical oversight&lt;/strong&gt; rather than hands-on engineering execution.&lt;br&gt;The Azure Cloud Architect will define cloud architecture standards, guide DevOps and engineering teams, and ensure Azure environments are designed for &lt;strong&gt;scalability, resilience, security, and compliance&lt;/strong&gt;. The architect will collaborate closely with engineering teams, program leadership, and government stakeholders to ensure cloud solutions align with mission objectives and federal security requirements.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: United States (Remote; DMV region preferred)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clearance Requirement&lt;/strong&gt;: U.S. Citizenship required; must currently hold or have previously held a Public Trust designation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Cloud Architecture &amp;amp; Strategy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and oversee &lt;strong&gt;highly available, secure, and scalable Azure architectures&lt;/strong&gt; across compute, storage, networking, and identity services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define &lt;strong&gt;enterprise Azure reference architectures, patterns, and best practices&lt;/strong&gt; for development teams.&

&lt;h1&gt;Product Manager&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About Pluribus Digital&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join us and do work that matters:&lt;/strong&gt; use your skills to improve how your government serves the public.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pluribus Digital partners with government customers to design, develop, and deliver impactful digital products. We are a hands-on digital services consultancy—part technologists, part change agents, and all heart. We employ modern engineering practices to solve complex challenges across healthcare, financial regulation, identity management, and digital government services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pluribus Digital is seeking a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to support the modernization of the &lt;strong&gt;Centers for Medicare &amp;amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) Health Insurance Oversight System (HIOS)&lt;/strong&gt;. This role is ideal for a product leader who thrives at the intersection of technology, data, and user needs while delivering mission-critical solutions that improve healthcare oversight and operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Product Manager, you&#39;ll partner with government stakeholders, engineers, architects, data specialists, and UX professionals to define product strategy and guide delivery across complex modernization initiatives. This role is highly collaborative and requires balancing business priorities, technical considerations, and data-driven decision making throughout the product lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The HIOS platform supports large volumes of regulatory and operational data, making this position especially well suited for someone with experience delivering data-intensive applications, modern APIs, reporting capabilities, and enterprise-scale software solutions in Agile environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applying modern Digital Services principles and human-centered design, you&#39;ll help ensure products are built around user needs, informed by data, and aligned with CMS mission objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are committed to continuous employee growth and upskilling, equipping our team with versatile, high-impact skills that drive success across multiple engagements throughout their careers at Pluribus.&lt;/p&gt;
