&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Define and communicate product vision, strategy, and roadmaps aligned with CMS modernization priorities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with government stakeholders to translate complex business and regulatory requirements into product outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prioritize features and capabilities based on mission impact, customer value, technical feasibility, and delivery timelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive product decisions using qualitative user feedback, operational metrics, and data insights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
