&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead cross-functional Agile teams through product planning, backlog refinement, sprint planning, and release activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop and maintain well-defined epics, user stories, and acceptance criteria.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate closely with engineering, architecture, UX, QA, and data teams throughout the software development lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support SAFe planning activities, including Program Increment (PI) Planning and roadmap alignment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
